  "detailed_description": "Mercenary Operator: Wolves is a 2D tactical top-down shooter that puts you into the shoes of a mercenary employed by Wolf, a private military company. Follow the Wolf PMC through their journey across a war-torn African country and elsewhere.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Play across several maps with randomized enemies and objectives for lots of replayability.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656740/extras/b3e28d1dd8031d7dd61cbd426334283b.poster.avif?t=1667530502\" width=500 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656740/extras/b3e28d1dd8031d7dd61cbd426334283b.webm?t=1667530502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656740/extras/b3e28d1dd8031d7dd61cbd426334283b.mp4?t=1667530502\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> Choose from a variety of different weapons.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656740/extras/1d092c25317124a6c20ff6ec59091111.poster.avif?t=1667530502\" width=500 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656740/extras/1d092c25317124a6c20ff6ec59091111.webm?t=1667530502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br></li><li> Customize your character and loadout.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656740/extras/f2e4c335ef245a727ff0c173b3cee940.poster.avif?t=1667530502\" width=500 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656740/extras/f2e4c335ef245